## Assembly Instructions
1. Glue the two top shade pieces together.  
2. Assemble the circuit according to the diagram.  
3. Insert the small stator pieces into the stator.  
4. Slide the stator and spacing ring onto the shaft.  
5. Press-fit the shaft into the rotor piece.  
6. Solder the shaft into the motor shaft and place the motor into its housing.  
7. Insert the motor, stator, rotor, and spacer ring assembly into the housing.  
8. Add circuitry, battery, and wintergreen oil sponge beneath the assembly.  
9. Insert the large spacer ring.  
10. Fit the storage container lid into the bottom, aligning tubes with holes.  
11. Screw the storage container into the housing.  
12. Attach the top component and secure a string for hanging.

